  "description": "Located in the sought-after Señorío De Aloha Urbanización, this beautifully appointed 4-bedroom apartment offers a perfect blend of modern living and Mediterranean charm. Ideal for families, groups, or those seeking a luxurious yet homely getaway, this property provides everything you need for a memorable stay in the heart of Nueva Andalucía.\n\nUpon entering, you’ll be welcomed into a bright and spacious living area, furnished with a comfortable seating arrangement and a dining area perfect for entertaining. Large windows and sliding glass doors flood the space with natural light, creating an open, airy feel throughout. The fully equipped kitchen is designed with convenience in mind, featuring modern appliances including an oven, microwave, dishwasher, and all necessary cookware—perfect for whipping up meals with ease.\n\nThe apartment boasts four generously sized bedrooms, each designed with comfort in mind. The master bedroom includes a very spacious en-suite shower room, while the second bedroom features its own en-suite bathroom. Bedrooms three and four share a well-appointed shower room, and there is also an additional guest toilet, making a total of four toilets throughout the property.\n\nThe standout feature of this property is the expansive terrace, providing ample outdoor space for al fresco dining, sunbathing, or simply relaxing with a glass of wine while taking in the views of the lush surroundings and gardens. The urbanization itself is equipped with beautiful, well-maintained gardens and multiple swimming pools, offering a resort-like atmosphere without leaving the comfort of home.\n\nConveniently located, Señorío De Aloha is just a short distance from Puerto Banús and the stunning beaches of Marbella. It’s also close to local supermarkets, trendy cafes, and the best golf courses in the area, making it the perfect base for exploring the Costa del Sol.\n\nPlease note that we welcome families and couples only, no groups under 30, and no hen or stag parties. Should you fall outside of this category but wish to book nonetheless, please send us an enquiry detailing a bit more about yourself and the group that you will be travelling with so we can request this for you.\n\nWe look forward to welcoming you!",
